
# 2_JSP九大内置对象


![image](data:image/png;base64,)
**四个域对象 **

pageContext  page域     当前页面内可用 

request       reqeust域  单次请求 

session       session域   单次会话 

application   application 域项目运行 

  

**响应对象** 

response   响应对象 

  

**输出流对象** 

out        打印流对象 

  

**其他三个对象** 

servletConfig:由于JSP本身也是一个Servlet,所以容器也会给我们准备一个ServletConfig 

page        就是他this对象 当前JSP对象本身   

exception   异常对象,在错误提示页上使用,当isErrorpage=true 才具有该对象 

##### 
九大内置对象的使用

Servlet代码 




1.  package com.msb.servlet;
2.  import com.msb.pojo.User;
3.  import javax.servlet.ServletContext;
4.  import javax.servlet.ServletException;
5.  import javax.servlet.annotation.WebServlet;
6.  import javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet;
7.  import javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest;
8.  import javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse;
9.  import javax.servlet.http.HttpSession;
10. import java.io.IOException;
11. import java.util.*;
12. /**
13.  * @Author: Ma HaiYang
14.  * @Description: MircoMessage:Mark_7001
15.  */
16. @WebServlet("/servlet1.do")
17. public class Servlet1 extends HttpServlet {
18.     @Override
19.     protected void service(HttpServletRequest req, HttpServletResponse
    resp) throws ServletException, IOException {
20.         // 向三个域中放入数据
21.         /*向请求域中放入数据*/
22.         User user=new User(1,"李雷","123456");
23.         req.setAttribute("user",user);
24.         req.setAttribute("msg","requestMessage");
25.         /*向session域中放入数据*/
26.         List<User> users =new ArrayList<>();
27.         User user1=new User(1,"韩梅梅","123456");
28.         User user2=new User(1,"小明","123456");
29.         User user3=new User(1,"小红","123456");
30.         Collections.addAll(users,user1,user2,user3);
31.         HttpSession session =   req.getSession();
32.         session.setAttribute("users",users);
33.         session.setAttribute("msg","sessionMessage");
34.         /*向application域中放入数据*/
35.         ServletContext application = getServletContext();
36.         Map<String,User> map =new HashMap<>();
37.         map.put("a",user1);
38.         map.put("b",user2);
39.         map.put("c",user3);
40.         application.setAttribute("userMap",map);
41.         application.setAttribute("msg","applicationMessage");
42.         // 跳转至jsp
43.         req.getRequestDispatcher("showInfo.jsp").forward(req,resp);
44.     }
45. }
